    "name": "Riven",
    "steam_appid": 1712350,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712350/extras/8fe82b57a90a96cf43e6d5c1f2df07d7.avif?t=1771535182\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>“我知道他在做什么…他在看着你。”<br><br>前往烈文，一个濒临崩溃边缘的美丽而神秘的世界。探索这一神秘地点，破解其谜题、揭晓其谜团、完成无畏救援，然后逃出生天。<br><br>拜访一个神秘世界<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712350/extras/b337207ef347e36de5180c67c539e956.poster.avif?t=1771535182\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712350/extras/b337207ef347e36de5180c67c539e956.webm?t=1771535182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712350/extras/b337207ef347e36de5180c67c539e956.mp4?t=1771535182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>“我叫格恩。我想你可能听说过我。”<br><br>《烈文》带你领略密不透风的丛林、令人惊叹的洞穴和庞然巨物。探索一个屈服于某人臆想的世界，这个人将自己视为神明。在这个世界里，每一步都沉浸在令人诧异的冒险之中。<br><br>沉浸于一片超现实的景致之中<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712350/extras/65d1abdaab5234d7b4dc154a474f9369.poster.avif?t=1771535182\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712350/extras/65d1abdaab5234d7b4dc154a474f9369.webm?t=1771535182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712350/extras/65d1abdaab5234d7b4dc154a474f9369.mp4?t=1771535182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>“你需要了解一大堆的历史…”<br><br>烈文赏识无微不至的观察。挑战烈文的狡黠谜题，这些谜题巧妙地布置在其整个叙事之中。随着你从看似支离破碎的信息中嗅出端倪，并了解这个世界的一切必知背景，烈文的环境将会揭示这个世界的故事。<br><br>揭开烈文的秘密<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712350/extras/189ca19a4692bf4ed5db0a552b4114f9.poster.avif?t=1771535182\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712350/extras/189ca19a4692bf4ed5db0a552b4114f9.webm?t=1771535182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712350/extras/189ca19a4692bf4ed5db0a552b4114f9.mp4?t=1771535182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>“…也许是时候回顾一下这个无法解释的谜团了。”<br><br>你在探险期间遇到的神秘岛屿居民是什么人？那个巨大的金圆顶有何作用？这个世界为何会濒临崩溃？游玩《烈文》并解答这些谜团——乃至更多费解谜题。<br><br>关于此次重制<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712350/extras/af1a5ad2b01200b5c063535e2263bacd.poster.avif?t=1771535182\" width=640 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712350/extras/af1a5ad2b01200b5c063535e2263bacd.webm?t=1771535182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712350/extras/af1a5ad2b01200b5c063535e2263bacd.mp4?t=1771535182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《烈文》取材于1997发布的热门原作，由传奇独立开发商Cyan Worlds倾力制作。该游戏得到了其关键原创想者的热心指导，在《神秘岛》宇宙的传奇叙事上加以拓展。<br><br>以前所未有的方式体验《烈文》——通过实时3D环境所赋予的自由移动能力。这一全新、重新构思和扩展版的《烈文》可提供更深邃的故事、新的极富感染力的视觉效果，以及一趟难忘的旅程——这趟旅程不仅忠实于原作，同时还扩展了烈文夺人心魄的世界。",
